  "body": "This PR contains the following updates:\n\n| Package | Type | Update | Change | References |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| rollup-plugin-node-resolve | devDependencies | patch | [`4.2.0` -> `4.2.1`](https://diff.intrinsic.com/rollup-plugin-node-resolve/4.2.0/4.2.1) | [source](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-node-resolve) |\n\n---\n\n### Release Notes\n\n<details>\n<summary>rollup/rollup-plugin-node-resolve</summary>\n\n### [`v4.2.1`](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-node-resolve/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#&#8203;421-2019-04-06)\n\n[Compare Source](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-node-resolve/compare/v4.2.0...v4.2.1)\n\n-   Respect setting the deprecated fields \"module\", \"main\", and \"jsnext\" ([#&#8203;204](https://togithub.com/rollup/rollup-plugin-node-resolve/pull/204) by [@&#8203;nick-woodward](https://togithub.com/nick-woodward))\n\n</details>\n\n---\n\n### Renovate configuration\n\n:date: **Schedule**: \"every weekend\" in timezone Europe/Paris.\n\n:vertical_traffic_light: **Automerge**: Enabled.\n\n:recycle: **Rebasing**: Whenever PR is stale, or if you modify the PR title to begin with \"`rebase!`\".\n\n:no_bell: **Ignore**: Close this PR and you won't be reminded about this update again.\n\n---\n\n - [ ] <!-- renovate-rebase -->If you want to rebase/retry this PR, check this box\n\n---\n\nThis PR has been generated by [Renovate Bot](https://togithub.com/marketplace/renovate). View repository job log [here](https://renovatebot.com/dashboard#algolia/instantsearch.js).",
